Title: slack: Fix ignored proxy option
Level: 1
Component: notifications
Compatible: incomp
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0p25
Date: 1620206289
Class: fix

With werk #12857 the option to configure a proxy for notification method "Slack
or Mattermost" was added.

However, this option was not taken into account in version 1.6.0p24 when
processing the notification.
